口述实录│儿子去了抗疫医疗一线，这是对他永生难忘的历练。
His son went to the first line of treatment against the disease. It was an unforgettable experience for him.
张家慧 王仲昀。
Wang Zhongyun, Zhang Jiahui.
新民周刊                      。
Xinmin Weekly.
新民周刊。
Xinmin Weekly.
